    "created_at": "2017-04-07T17:26:34Z",
    "updated_at": "2017-04-07T17:27:32Z",
    "body": "I have also encountered the same issue. With Electron 1.6.2, uv_idle/uv_prepare do not work inside of a native node module. When loading the same native node module with NodeJS they do work. I am able to get around the issue by using uv_async to call code on the default loop as the author of this bug suggests."
